narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Find a great professor, and this independent research structure is great.
I would definitely recommend doing this! This is real-life experience that's extremely interesting (if you make it interesting and educational).

You get out of research what you put in. This may not be a structured class, but there is a lot to gain from self-motivating yourself to do literature reviews in your subject of interest, think deeply about possible experimental designs, and help your lab carry out its studies.
Fantastic course, really depends on your advisor. Allows you to pursue original research.
